  <h1>About Malawi Hidden Gems</h1>
  <p>This blog is a community platform where travelers and locals share stories, tips, and adventures from across Malawi.
    Our goal is to showcase the beauty, culture, and people of the Warm Heart of Africa.</p>

  <h2>What You'll Find Here</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Cultural stories</li>
    <li>Adventure highlights</li>
    <li>Personal experiences from contributors</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How Posting Works</h2>
  <p>Anyone can create and publish a post without creating an account. Each new post gets a private editor token stored in the creator's browser so only that contributor can edit or delete it later.</p>
